# App (Ionic PWA)

- Primary target is PWA; Ionic/Capacitor artifacts may remain
- Do not refactor Ionic unless explicitly requested
- Minimal UI overlap with `apps/dert-web/` — keep apps independent

## Commands
```bash
npm run app:build
npm run app:lint
npm run app:test
```
